530
00:38:25,230 --> 00:38:27,910
to breathe through?!

531
00:38:27,910 --> 00:38:30,910
Wow, was I the hole that you breathed through?

532
00:38:30,910 --> 00:38:34,990
I feel emotional but at the same time suddenly burdened....Noona!
