539
00:38:53,880 --> 00:38:56,840
will you be satisfied with the results?

540
00:39:16,200 --> 00:39:20,300
Noona, I toured around Central and South America.

541
00:39:22,180 --> 00:39:24,190
She's a girl I dated in Cuba.

542
00:39:25,680 --> 00:39:29,710
And she's a girl I met at the Samba Festival in Brazil named Priscilla.

543
00:39:30,880 --> 00:39:32,630
And this is my friend from college,

544
00:39:32,630 --> 00:39:34,270
they got married in Mexico.

545
00:39:34,270 --> 00:39:36,970
They married within one week of meeting.

546
00:39:43,610 --> 00:39:47,780
These two, while I was taking their pictures, the kids there...

547
00:40:01,020 --> 00:40:03,270
Mom is well, right?

548
00:40:04,130 --> 00:40:05,510
