555
00:40:33,440 --> 00:40:35,980
It's a disappointment, Hyung.

556
00:40:35,980 --> 00:40:38,900
Even if Father said something, you should have cut him off.

557
00:40:38,900 --> 00:40:40,570
You're the only one I depended on.

558
00:40:40,570 --> 00:40:43,000
It's not because I received the request.

559
00:40:43,000 --> 00:40:46,420
I okay'd it because you had potential.

560
00:40:46,420 --> 00:40:49,170
Aiyoo, if you say it like that then...

561
00:40:49,170 --> 00:40:53,530
