562
00:40:53,530 --> 00:40:56,580
Because I taught you well.

563
00:40:56,580 --> 00:41:00,090
Who was the tutor that taught a naive middle schooler
about alcohol?

564
00:41:00,090 --> 00:41:04,370
Who was the cocky and absurd middle schooler
who rebelled against a naive college student?

565
00:41:05,290 --> 00:41:07,350
At that time, soju was an anesthetic to you.

566
00:41:07,350 --> 00:41:10,130
You calmed down a little after you learned soju from me.

567
00:41:10,130 --> 00:41:14,060
I admit it. At that time, I was a little immature.

568
00:41:14,060 --> 00:41:16,940
It's a relief that I met you then, Hyung.

569
00:41:16,940 --> 00:41:18,700
Cheers.

570
00:41:27,570 --> 00:41:31,560
But Hyung, over there that woman,

571
00:41:32,780 --> 00:41:36,640
