572
00:41:40,560 --> 00:41:42,870
She's looking at me.

573
00:41:43,770 --> 00:41:45,310
It's me.
- I'm telling you, it's me.

574
00:41:45,330 --> 00:41:47,920
She was looking at me all along since I got here and
was waiting for you.

575
00:41:47,950 --> 00:41:49,750
Ai, really.

576
00:41:49,780 --> 00:41:51,110
There's no basis for this argument!

577
00:41:51,150 --> 00:41:52,660
Do you want to make a bet?

578
00:41:52,700 --> 00:41:54,460
Deal.

579
00:42:01,200 --> 00:42:03,060
Why?

580
00:42:04,350 --> 00:42:07,830
You're nervous because it's the first time
you've seen a celebrity, huh?

581
00:42:07,830 --> 00:42:10,480
Omo, so cute.

582
00:42:10,480 --> 00:42:12,920
Oh, I...

583
00:42:17,940 --> 00:42:20,100
The thing is...

584
00:42:21,390 --> 00:42:24,450
